properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS - MASCOT O'Riordan Street between Baxter Road AND Joyce Drive
properties.otherAdvice:

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS Due to damaged bridge - CHARLEYLONG/TOMBOYE Charleylong Bridge and Nerriga Road between Tomboye Road AND Stewarts Crossing Road
properties.otherAdvice: This bridge is closed until further notice whilst repairs are undertaken.
properties.diversions:
The primary detour route (vehicles under 15 tonnes) is via Oallen Rd, Sandy Point Rd, Cullala Rd, Lumley Rd, Braidwood Rd and Kings Hwy, in both directions, adding around 35 minutes travel time.  

Light vehicles can also use Charleys Forrest Rd and Little River Rd between Nerriga and Braidwood.

Heavy vehicles should use the Kings Hwy, or other approved routes depending on their load limit restriction.

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS traffic changes and long term road closures - BADGERYS CREEK Elizabeth Dr/Badgerys Creek Rd near Lawson Road
properties.otherAdvice:
As part of the Western Sydney Airport Project, there is traffic changes and long term road closures to complete the ultimate design of Elizabeth Dr and Badgerys Creek Rd.

The following traffic changes are in operation:

Traffic has switched to a newly constructed Badgerys Creek Rd. This new Badgerys Creek link Rd will join Elizabeth Dr.
• Existing Badgerys Creek Rd is closed permanently between Elizabeth Dr and Pitt St.

Elizabeth Dr traffic has been switched over to the newly constructed carriageway.
• A new roundabout at the intersection of Elizabeth Dr and the new link of Badgerys Creek Rd which has been shifted and realigned.
• Barriers are placed eastbound along Elizabeth Dr and the roundabout to complete pavement works on the existing Elizabeth Dr.
properties.displayName: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS traffic changes and long term road closures

properties.headline: CHANGED TRAFFIC CONDITIONS from 8am Jan 25 - ST PETERS Campbell Street, May Street, Brown Street, Florence Street, and Hutchinson Street at St Peters
properties.otherAdvice:
• Traffic changes start from 8am Saturday 25 January.
  • Traffic movements in all direction in place at the intersection of May St, Campbell St, Unwins Bridge Rd and Bedwin Rd.
  • Access to Brown St from Campbell St travelling westbound only. At the Campbell St intersection, left in/left out access only on Brown St. No right turn allowed into or out of Brown St.
  • Access to Florence St from Campbell St travelling westbound only. At the Campbell St intersection, left in/left out access only on Florence St. No right turn allowed into or out of Florence St.  
  • Access to Hutchinson St from Campbell St travelling eastbound only. At the Campbell St intersection, left in access only on Hutchinson St. No right turn allowed into Hutchinson St.    
  • A new signalised pedestrian crossing will be operational at the intersection of Bedwin Rd and Campbell St.
